name: WhitepaperMIX
description:
该模型是以novelai官方animesfw-latest模型202fcec0(旧版短哈希值)为底部模型融合而来

因为是以官方模型为基础所以会出现画面崩坏的情况，在其他模型可以使用的prompt可能需要重新调整，但是使用得当会有一些意想不到的效果

高清修复推荐使用R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

该模型可以不使用vae

2023/6/29

更新了V1 fp16版本

2023/7/3

更新了V2版本

This model is based on the fusion of Novelai's official animesfw latest model 202fcec0 (old version short hash value) as the bottom model

Because it is based on the official model, there may be screen crashes. Prompts that can be used in other models may need to be readjusted, but using them properly can have some unexpected effects

Recommended use of R-ESRGAN 4x+Anime6B for high-definition repair

This model may not use vae

June 29, 2023

Updated V1 fp16 version

July 3, 2023

Updated V2 version

modelVersions.name: v2
modelVersions.description: V2在保留泛用性的同时降低了崩图的概率以及严重程度
